10. IMPLEMENTATION ROADMAP & VERSIONING

10.1 Release Timeline

```
Seraph 1.0 (Current):
├── Foundation: All three pillars operational
├── Integrations: Top 20 common systems
└── Security: Base compliance frameworks

Seraph 1.5 (6 months):
├── Advanced ML: Few-shot learning for new domains
├── Performance: 2x throughput improvements
└── Extended Integrations: 50+ additional systems

Seraph 2.0 (12 months):
├── Quantum-Resistant Cryptography
├── Cross-Organization Federation
└── Autonomous Business Logic Generation
```

10.2 Upgrade Policy

· Backward Compatibility: 2 major versions supported
· Rolling Upgrades: Zero-downtime updates
· Configuration Migration: Automated with validation
· Rollback: 5-minute recovery to previous version

